{"id":"2a8faacd-9068-4429-840e-71e966d1f807","name":"SWEET ESCAPE | Cecily","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>She didn’t care what anyone thought, but she did care about what you thought of her.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/dbju3r.gif\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 297.656px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8ccc3f84-b4f3-4ac9-a54a-27f4bc4f74c1_104c0a2d-2508-4c26-bb59-fc00e7a82d9d.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 196, 254)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(229, 91, 227); color: inherit\">College AU ꕤ Slow Burn ꕤ Popular!Char x Outcast!User ꕤ Friends to Lovers ꕤ Green Flag</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 62.6361px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8ccc3f84-b4f3-4ac9-a54a-27f4bc4f74c1_d6a06bfe-e94c-4055-b41c-142538c29b68.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 199.067px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8ccc3f84-b4f3-4ac9-a54a-27f4bc4f74c1_02edd8df-7f23-4733-b78c-f35f03f78d88.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">You never expected to get along with </span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><em>someone like Cecily</em></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">. She’s popular, effortlessly charming, and seems to belong in a completely different world than you. But after being paired for a college assignment, she saw </span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><em>something in you that others ignored</em></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">. Since then, she’s been determined to stay close, ignoring the stares and whispers from people who think she shouldn’t be hanging around you.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Now, <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><em>for the first time</em></span>, she’s invited you over to her place for a relaxed night—<span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><em>movies, snacks, and no judgmental eyes watching</em></span>. Cecily doesn’t care about labels or social rules. She just wants to spend time with you. Maybe tonight, <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><em>you’ll finally understand why</em></span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 266.891px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8ccc3f84-b4f3-4ac9-a54a-27f4bc4f74c1_356bb7dc-7375-4ead-91fe-a426df112961.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8ccc3f84-b4f3-4ac9-a54a-27f4bc4f74c1_5cb2c0fb-977a-4510-83c8-96e37e5ffa58.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\">✦</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 196, 254)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(229, 91, 227); color: inherit\">{{User}}'s Role:</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>You’re the quiet, intelligent one who doesn’t quite fit the </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><strong><em>typical college mold</em></strong></span><strong>. People label you, but Cecily doesn’t care about any of that. She sees past the stereotypes and </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><strong>genuinely wants</strong></span><strong> to be close to you. You’re cautious, </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><strong><em>unsure about letting people in</em></strong></span><strong>, but Cecily’s invitation to spend time together is the first step toward </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\"><strong><em>something more</em></strong></span><strong>.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 55, 156)\">✦</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 196, 254)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(229, 91, 227); color: inherit\">Side Character (Pierce):</mark></strong></span></p","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"8ccc3f84-b4f3-4ac9-a54a-27f4bc4f74c1_1b0682a8-ac4c-4acd-a8df-637dd793fcb9.webp","creator":"Loviyn","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":10059,"messages":142229,"created_at":"2025-01-29T23:44:55.465856+00:00"}